{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ff68b1c0f7","title":"省、市委书记会议上各同志提出的问题","origin":"根据文件翻印件打印。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"28d033f7af","index":0,"year":1957,"month":1,"day":20,"articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7fc5fd78be","name":"中共中央办公厅"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"137877c561","type":"title","text":"省、市委书记会议上各同志提出的问题","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"ecd3bd1557","type":"authors","text":"中共中央办公厅","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"1c5e343a58","type":"appellation","text":"刘仁：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"b4bbe6e70f","type":"paragraph","text":"一、现在的工资制度和技术等级标准都有不合理的地方，需要统盘加以研究。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"c9e3d1a639","type":"paragraph","text":"二、在不增加人的条件下，可否每年给工人一个回家的时间，以免进城的家属太多，而缓和宿舍的修建难于满足需要的紧张状况。现有的福利、奖金、救济等制度对工人家属进城，起着鼓励的作用，应当加以改变。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"075f49dd26","type":"paragraph","text":"三、大城市周围的农村，应当有计划地多养些猪。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"9bb58bd2e6","type":"appellation","text":"张德生：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"462d0f4643","type":"paragraph","text":"一、农业合作化以后，基层组织的调整，基层干部的分工，需要加以研究。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"02e6fea727","type":"paragraph","text":"二、西安市的直接影响生产的公用事业的建设项目，在削减投资的时候需要加以照顾。厂矿区的学校、商店等方面的投资由谁负责，希望明确规定。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"660099b530","type":"paragraph","text":"三、在减少和推迟建设项目的时候，应当好好地注意人员的处理和设备的维护。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"bbe6451912","type":"paragraph","text":"四、希望多调一些废钢材给地方。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"827ca78dbb","type":"paragraph","text":"五、商业的管理人员太多，有些机构可以合并，甚至取消，例如粮食的供应人员可以减少，有些门市部可以撤销。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"fdf25fdf44","type":"paragraph","text":"六、关于党政人员的减薪问题，可以有两种办法：一种是全面减薪，一种是，减少以至取消各种供给制的残余，如伙夫的编制、取暖费、生活补贴等。比较起来，后一办法较好些。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"35939bdbeb","type":"paragraph","text":"七、农村供销社和信用社，是否可以吸收些地主、富农的游资。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"46dff4f1b7","type":"appellation","text":"王任重：","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"dd24dc1f83","type":"paragraph","text":"一、国家对农产品的预购，不要减少，仍予以维持。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"4ba8d4e84d","type":"paragraph","text":"二、三峡的勘探、设计工作是否继续进行，希望中央有明确的方针。长江水利委员会和湖北省委的意见是：第二个五年计划准备，第三个五年计划施工，第五个五年计划完成。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"94b935e396","type":"paragraph","text":"三、产棉区的农业税现在只占农产值的百分之五，可以适当增加。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"49c16d6fae","type":"appellation","text":"吴芝圃：","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"37011f8727","type":"paragraph","text":"一、农业合作化的优越性应该继续加以宣传。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"e0bc60db77","type":"paragraph","text":"二、希望对河南省多增加一些民用煤，用赊销的办法贷放一些水车。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"},{"id":"cc59468108","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央办公厅机要室　一九五七年一月二十一日发","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7"}],"page":{"id":"1c8fb71f7c","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ff68b1c0f7","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}